---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="How We Work | Enablement Engineering" description="AI systems that produce evidence, not just outputs. For teams where 'the AI said so' isn't an acceptable answer.">
	<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Header -->
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">
					How We Work
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					AI systems that produce evidence, not just outputs. For teams where "the AI said so" isn't an acceptable answer.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- The Reality -->
			<div class="card-base p-8 lg:p-12 mb-12 bg-neutral-50">
				<p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 mb-6">
					If you've been asked to "implement AI" without a clear answer for how you'll audit it, explain it to regulators, or defend it when something goes wrong—you're in the right place.
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-neutral-700">
					Most AI implementations fail in one of two ways: <strong class="text-ink">black boxes that work until they don't</strong> (and when they fail, no one can explain why), or <strong class="text-ink">systems that sit unused</strong> because teams don't trust outputs they can't verify.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- The Core Insight: Why Procedures Matter -->
			<div class="card-base p-8 lg:p-12 mb-12 off-kilter-0-5">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">The Core Insight</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-ink font-semibold mb-6">
					The procedures are the audit trail.
				</p>
				<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-neutral-700 mb-8">
					<p>
						When an agent calls a tool, it's quantizing fuzzy natural language into a discrete, auditable operation. Every tool call is evidence that the system:
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg">
						<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-ink">Understood intent correctly</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">It parsed what you wanted</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg">
						<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-ink">Routed to the right procedure</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">It matched intent to a known, tested process</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg">
						<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-ink">Produced auditable output</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">The result came from documented steps with logged evidence</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-secondary-900 text-neutral-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
					<p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">
						Teams don't scale on clever prompting. They scale on standardized procedures with governance.
					</p>
					<p class="text-neutral-300">
						For accessibility and compliance work, this isn't optional. The procedures ARE the audit trail.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- The Framework -->
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
				<a href="/writing/core-four-framework" class="card-base p-6 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors group no-underline">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-600">The Core Four Framework</h3>
					<p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
						Context, Model, Prompt, and Tools—the four elements of every agentic system. Tools are where trust lives.
					</p>
					<span class="text-primary-600 font-medium">Read the framework →</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/definitions/enablement-engineering" class="card-base p-6 hover:border-primary-300 transition-colors group no-underline">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-600">The Operating Method</h3>
					<p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">
						Intent → Translation → Orchestration → Execution → Evidence → Learning. Six phases that close the loop.
					</p>
					<span class="text-primary-600 font-medium">See the full methodology →</span>
				</a>
			</div>

			<!-- Glass Box AI -->
			<div class="card-base p-8 lg:p-12 mb-12 bg-neutral-50 off-kilter-neg-0-5">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">Glass Box, Not Black Box</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-8">
					We build systems where reasoning is visible, not just outputs.
				</p>

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
						</svg>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Visible procedures</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">See which procedure was called and why</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
						</svg>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Surfaced errors</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Error states are visible, not hidden</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
						</svg>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Human oversight</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Human judgment built into the loop</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
						</svg>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Audit trails</h3>
							<p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Documentation that survives compliance review</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p class="text-neutral-700">
					Black box AI might work for low-stakes applications. For accessibility, legal compliance, or anywhere you need to explain decisions to auditors, regulators, or skeptical stakeholders—you need glass box.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- What You Get -->
			<div class="card-base p-8 lg:p-12 mb-12 off-kilter-0-5">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-6">What You Get</h2>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
						<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Evidence that survives audit</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Logs, traces, and documentation you can show to regulators.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
						<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Systems that explain themselves</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Language you can use when legal asks "how does this work?"</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
						<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Procedures you own</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Portable, modifiable, improvable. No vendor lock-in.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
						<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">A path to independence</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Built for you to own and extend. The goal is to not need us.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- CTA -->
			<div class="text-center py-12 border-t border-neutral-200">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">
					Ready to see this in action?
				</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 mb-8">
					Explore our services or see the methodology applied in real projects.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
					<a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold bg-accent-500 text-secondary-900 hover:bg-accent-600 h-12 px-10 no-underline">
						See Our Services
					</a>
					<a href="/work" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold bg-secondary-900 text-neutral-50 hover:bg-secondary-800 h-12 px-10 no-underline">
						View Projects
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
